layout: null
permalink: /ja/sitemap.xml
---

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">

  {%- comment -%}
  일본어 홈(index) 추가
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <url>
    <loc>{{ site.url }}/ja/</loc>
    <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>
    <priority>1.0</priority>
  </url>

  {%- comment -%}
  파일명에 "-ja"가 들어간 포스트만 일본어 글로 간주해서 추가
  예: /_posts/2025-12-09-tesla-fsd-grok-explained-ja.md
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign ja_posts = site.posts | where_exp: "post", "post.path contains '-ja.'" -%}
  {%- for post in ja_posts -%}
    <url>
      <loc>{{ site.url }}{{ post.url }}</loc>
      <lastmod>{{ post.last_modified_at | default: post.date | date_to_xmlschema }}</lastmod>
      <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>
      <priority>0.7</priority>
    </url>
  {%- endfor -%}

  {%- comment -%}
  혹시 /ja/ 밑에 별도 페이지(예: /ja/about/, /ja/contact/) 있으면 같이 포함
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign ja_pages = site.pages | where_exp: "page", "page.path contains 'ja/'" -%}
  {%- for page in ja_pages -%}
    {%- if page.url != '/ja/' and page.url != '/ja/sitemap.xml' -%}
    <url>
      <loc>{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}</loc>
      <changefreq>monthly</changefreq>
      <priority>0.5</priority>
    </url>
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}

</urlset>
